Sunshine State;;57;;80;;PG-13;;This drama tells the story of a Florida island besieged by country-club resort developers. Included in the story are a woman (Angela Bassett) returning home after a long absence, and another woman (Edie Falco) who is forced to sell the restaurant and motel she inherited.;;Drama;;John Sayles;;2002;;Edie Falco,Angela Bassett,Jane Alexander,Ralph Waite,James McDaniel,Timothy Hutton,Mary Alice,Bill Cobbs,Mary Steenburgen,Alex Lewis,Gordon Clapp,Richard Edson,Tom Wright,Perry Lang,Miguel Ferrer,Marc Blucas,Michael Greyeyes,Alan King,Charlayne Woodard;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sunshine_state